Package: arrayQualityMetrics
Title: Quality metrics on ExpressionSets
Version: 1.3.0
Author: Audrey Kauffmann, Wolfgang Huber
Maintainer: Audrey Kauffmann <audrey@ebi.ac.uk>
Depends: R (>= 2.6.0), Biobase (>= 1.15.13), geneplotter (>= 1.15.2), genefilter(>= 1.15.6), vsn (>= 3.0.10), RColorBrewer, affyPLM, simpleaffy, CCl4 (>= 1.0.4), lattice, latticeExtra, grid
Description: This package performs quality metrics on ExpressionSet containing 
	microarray data from any platforms, one or two channels. 
	The results are designated to allow the user to rapidly assess the
	quality of a set of arrays.
License: LGPL version 2 or newer
biocViews: Microarray, QualityControl
